info:
  title: Users
  version: '1.0'
paths:

      parameters:
        - name: active
          in: query

          required: false
          schema:
            type: boolean
          examples:
            For active users:
              summary: Get only active users
              value: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: query parameter active'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
